1 0 0 1 50 800 Tm () Tj
1 0 0 1 50 786 Tm (UBUNTU EC2 SETUP COMMANDS) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 772 Tm () Tj
1 0 0 1 50 758 Tm (Run these on the app EC2 host:) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 744 Tm () Tj
1 0 0 1 50 730 Tm (sudo apt update) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 716 Tm (sudo apt install -y python3 python3-venv python3-pip nginx git curl) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 702 Tm (cd /opt) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 688 Tm (sudo git clone <your-repo-url> Trading) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 674 Tm (sudo chown -R $USER:$USER /opt/Trading) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 660 Tm (cd /opt/Trading) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 646 Tm (python3 -m venv venv) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 632 Tm (source venv/bin/activate) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 618 Tm (pip install --upgrade pip) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 604 Tm (pip install -r requirements.txt) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 590 Tm (pip install fastapi "uvicorn[standard]" python-multipart) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 576 Tm () Tj
1 0 0 1 50 562 Tm (RECOMMENDED SWAP SETUP) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 548 Tm () Tj
1 0 0 1 50 534 Tm (sudo fallocate -l 2G /swapfile) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 520 Tm (sudo chmod 600 /swapfile) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 506 Tm (sudo mkswap /swapfile) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 492 Tm (sudo swapon /swapfile) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 478 Tm (free -h) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 464 Tm () Tj
1 0 0 1 50 450 Tm (Persist swap:) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 436 Tm (echo '/swapfile none swap sw 0 0' | sudo tee -a /etc/fstab) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 422 Tm () Tj
1 0 0 1 50 408 Tm (POSTGRESQL DATABASE SETUP) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 394 Tm () Tj
1 0 0 1 50 380 Tm (Use Amazon RDS PostgreSQL.) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 366 Tm () Tj
1 0 0 1 50 352 Tm (Recommended baseline:) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 338 Tm (- engine: PostgreSQL 16) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 324 Tm (- instance: db.t3.small minimum) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 310 Tm (- storage: gp3) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 296 Tm (- public access: disabled) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 282 Tm (- Multi-AZ: enabled for production) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 268 Tm () Tj
1 0 0 1 50 254 Tm (Create:) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 240 Tm (- database name: vinayak) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 226 Tm (- user: vinayak_app) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 212 Tm () Tj
1 0 0 1 50 198 Tm (POSTGRESQL CONNECTION STRING) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 184 Tm () Tj
1 0 0 1 50 170 Tm (SQLAlchemy style:) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 156 Tm (postgresql+psycopg2://vinayak_app:YOUR_PASSWORD@YOUR_RDS_ENDPOINT:5432/vinayak) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 142 Tm () Tj
1 0 0 1 50 128 Tm (Direct psycopg style:) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 114 Tm (postgresql://vinayak_app:YOUR_PASSWORD@YOUR_RDS_ENDPOINT:5432/vinayak) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 100 Tm () Tj
1 0 0 1 50 86 Tm (ENVIRONMENT FILE EXAMPLE) Tj
ET
